      h1 Gumba

      p
        | Gumba is the tool which gives you ability to use CoffeeScript and
        = ' '
        a(href="https://github.com/epeli/underscore.string")  underscore.string
        = ' '
        | goodness right inside your command line. Think of it as of modern variation of
        = ' '
        code awk
        = ' '
        | or
